page.title: 16WILD LIFE AT N.CAVE FISHPOND
page.content: Survey taken on July 20th 1985 (ref.891324)at N.Cave fishponds. The day was sunny and warm BIRDS: Canada Geese, Common (white) geese, Mallard Ducks INSECTS: Meadow Brown Butterfly, Blue Dancer Fly, Grass Moth WATER CREATURES: Water Snail, Mites May Fly Nymph, Red Worm, Water Boatman, Diving Beetle, Water Beetle (Two species) PLANTS: Reed Mace, Hard Rush, Water Forget-me-not, Spike Rush, Water mint, Sweet Grass, Marsh Bedstraw, Water Plantain,Reed Grass, Branched Burr Weed, Jointed Rush, Fool's Watercress Great Hairy Willow Herb, Sharp Dock, Gypsy Wort, Mud Water Starwort, Great Pond Sedge, Marsh arrow Grass, Common Duck Weed, Marsh Bird's Foot Trefoil
